## The Plagues of Egypt – Biblical AI Cinematic  
[▶ Watch Video](https://youtube.com/shorts/ALOX75GWGS0?feature=share)  
**Description:**  
An epic AI-generated visual interpretation of the Plagues of Egypt from the Book of Exodus. This cinematic short brings the ancient story to life with intense, high-definition imagery of divine judgment, Pharaoh’s resistance, and the supernatural signs that shook a nation.
